lead_paragraph: The many red-and-yellow-clad Romanian fans at Uniprix Stadium got what they came for Sunday when Simona Halep beat Madison Keys in the Rogers Cup final.

headline.print_headline: Halep Beats Keys 7-6 (2), 6-3 in Montreal Final
